ven at the eleventh hour? </div><div class="t m905 x59 he y1725 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Verse 6. </div><div class="t m286 x29 he y18a6 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8. </div><div class="t m1bc x66 he y19d ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What excuse was offered by the idlers in the market place </div><div class="t m718 x59 he y1898 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">at a time when the need for workers was so great? </div><div class="t m904 x59 he y1989 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Verses 6, 7. </div><div class="t mc43 x29 he y687 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">9: Of what avail was such an excuse? Verse 7, last part. </div><div class="t m54a x59 he y1d34 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Note 3. </div><div class="t m41c x74 he yb3c ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">10. </div><div class="t m6db x6f he y1a92 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What follows the eleventh-hour call? Verse 8. Note 4. </div><div class="t m41c x73 he y1da0 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">11. </div><div class="t m8f x6f he y1cd7 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How did the Saviour refer to the approaching night, which </div><div class="t ma58 x59 he yfa0 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">would end Christian service? John 9: 4. </div><div class="t m41c x73 he y1745 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">12. </div><div class="t m89d x6f he y1f30 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How is the work of the Lord to be finished? Rom. 9: 28. </div><div class="t m41c x73 he y16d2 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">13. </div><div class="t m85d x6f he y16d2 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">To how many of the followers of Christ has work been as-</div><div class="t m445 x59 he y1873 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">signed? Mark 13: 34. Note 5. </div><div class="t m41c x73 he y69 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">14. </div><div class="t me8b x6f he y1634 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In the final reckoning, what will be the result if bestowed </div><div class="t m1f2f x49 he y1594 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">talent has been hidden and the assigned work neg-</div><div class="t m83c x49 he y134e ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lected? Matt. 25: 24-30. </div><div c